Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.36,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs10\c&H4F615F&\3c&HC1E7E8&\fax0.3\frz30.64\pos(217.5,125.5)}Sasaki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.36,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H6B4D40&\fax0.43\pos(386.5,201)\frz28.42}Wholesome Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.24,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,又到了每年最恐怖的季节。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:14.62,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,到这个年纪体检就开始吓人了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.04,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,哦哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:22.75,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,搞什么啊你去年体检全是B以上。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.34,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你有收到什么提醒吗铃木？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:28.42,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,尿酸和中性脂肪。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.76,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,销售员常有的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:35.14,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,但是！今年我不一样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:38.39,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,因为从去年体检之后。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.94,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,我一直吃亲爱的惠子酱做的健康便当！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.90,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,锵锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.36,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,量好大啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.15,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(193,1)\fscx90\fnArial Black\c&H2E372F&\frz15.45\fax0.65\pos(453,205)}Hang in there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.15,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,没错我会加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.24,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这就是爱啊纯粹的爱。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.33,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:59.83,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,为了不辜负她的爱。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:02.92,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,体检之前我戒烟戒酒。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.59,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,开饭了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:07.42,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,喝酒就算了抽烟也戒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:13.01,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,嗯我想和惠子酱白头偕老。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.48,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,得好好咀嚼。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:25.94,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs13\fnTimes New Roman\c&H606876&\frz-21.31\fax-0.3\pos(417,150)}Are you a regular smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:25.94,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs13\fnTimes New Roman\c&H606876&\frz-21.31\fax-0.3\pos(456,209)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:25.94,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs13\fnTimes New Roman\c&H606876&\frz-21.31\fax-0.3\pos(522,240)}No
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.99,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,一共1,160日元。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:31.90,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.83,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,找零和收据。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.21,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,还有这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:46.79,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,新出了个无酒精啤酒有优惠。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:47.88,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,需要的话请用。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.46,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我马上要体检了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.60,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,正考虑换无酒精饮料喝一阵。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.97,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这个帮大忙了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.89,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.87,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,晚上好田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.38,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哟快体检了还来抽烟的人来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:51.88,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.67,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你、你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.30,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,山田小姐告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.76,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,对对从山田小姐那儿听说的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.26,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,Sa-slow-ki。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯马上就到了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.90,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我已经减量了好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.90,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,失礼了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.74,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,减量？减了一两根吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:19.28,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯……是的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.62,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,超市员工也有体检吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:33.42,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯应该也快了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:38.80,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那你也要提前减量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.80,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,减量……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.55,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(560,1)\bord1.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H6522EB&\3c&H5A27C5&\frz339.6\fsp5\pos(195,212.5)}fl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.55,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(560,1)\bord1.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H6522EB&\3c&H5A27C5&\fsp5\pos(467,216)}ab...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.89,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我只喝一勺汤。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:47.89,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,当然。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.23,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.56,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,毕竟健康就是财富。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:55.23,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不好好保重身体就没法工作了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:58.57,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,说得好田山小姐真帅。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.32,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,再看看我自己多可悲。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.95,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,光想着临时抱佛脚不彻底戒酒。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.71,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不过你今天吃很多啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:16.21,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,每年医生都让我增重。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:21.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但就是胖不起来。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:25.51,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能容易长肉就好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.51,DefaultOverlap,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,揪。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.85,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,干、干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.39,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你真的皮包骨啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.39,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田、田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:36.73,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我们熟食区有好东西多吃点长肉。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好、好的谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.78,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不过……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.12,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,最有害的东西没戒掉。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:47.45,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,其他都是临时抱佛脚。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.66,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,可不是嘛。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.92,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但如果医生说必须戒烟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.09,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你会戒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:57.84,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.72,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这个嘛……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.18,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,如果必须戒的话。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:08.14,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那就麻烦了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,毕竟。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.06,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,{\pos(205,342)}组长他——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.06,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,{\pos(456,342)}你上司……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.85,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,还是会骂你。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.44,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是啊我肯定受不了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.95,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯我也不好戒。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真到那一步就完了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.33,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,没事的。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:37.58,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,好了现在你有了无敌的身体。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.51,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:51.72,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,感觉我一直想太多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.44,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,现在清醒了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.48,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,都是托田山小姐的福……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.40,FlashbackItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但如果医生说必须戒烟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.45,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那当然只能……戒了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.38,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fs11\c&H70686A&\frz2.523\fax-0.05\pos(380.5,250)\4c&H635D60&\shad0.5}Wholesome Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.38,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs10\frz1.593\fax-0.05\pos(108,283.5)}Chill Pharmacy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.41,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs10\c&H4F615F&\3c&HC1E7E8&\fax0.3\frz30.64\pos(220.5,129.5)}Sasaki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.41,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4A3DB8&\frz27.18\fax0.43\pos(245.5,147.5)}Private
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.41,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4A3DB8&\frz27.18\fax0.43\pos(312.5,135.5)}Results Enclosed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.41,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H6B4D40&\fax0.43\frz27.78\clip(m 325 237 l 433 150 441 193 347 251)\pos(390.5,204)}Wholesome Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.41,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,呀吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:08:00.96,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,尿酸和中性脂肪正常值！A等！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.42,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,等等为什么比去年胖了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:08.34,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,不管了得告诉惠子酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.26,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,咔嚓咔嚓。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.18,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(446,150)\fs18\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H575553&\3c&HF6F6F4&\b0\pos(270,73)}Very Healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.68,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,回头告诉我你结果怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.81,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,我去抽根烟！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.36,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.32,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,体检结果怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.78,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,怎么了？你那烂上司又搞事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:36.70,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不是是我身体烂。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.50,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.87,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.55,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,抽烟真的对身体不好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:54.43,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,佐佐木君的体检说要进一步检查和治疗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.35,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,肺部？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.64,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,太遗憾了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.60,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,所以他要戒烟了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.06,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,那当然。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.11,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,怎么了山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:10.86,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,他没有理由再来那里了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.41,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,山田。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.87,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,如果佐佐木君发现某人有意外的一面。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.87,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,他是那种接受不了的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.04,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,他不是那种人。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.71,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,那你只需要说。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:28.84,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,「其实二号收银台一直是我」。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.88,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,这样就不用找借口见面了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.39,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,不过……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.14,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,他心中山田小姐的女神形象会碎一地。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.18,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,但也会开始看到真实的你。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:47.44,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,喂山田你在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.94,DefaultOverlap,CUSTOMER,0,0,0,,打扰了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.61,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,请问需要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.70,Default,CUSTOMER,0,0,0,,请帮我包一下这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:53.28,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,好的马上。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.87,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我知道。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.62,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,那为什么……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.25,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我为什么在慌？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.13,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs16\bord2\c&HE6E0DB&\3c&H573DA9&\frz9.13\fax-0.15\pos(142.5,140)}24-Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.13,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fnArial Black\bord2\c&H2E0EAD&\3c&HF1E9E8&\fax-0.1\frz6.38\4c&H85634B&\shad2\pos(305.5,165)}Supermarket S
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.93,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,终于休息一天。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.22,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,明天去趟医院吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.86,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,也得找时间去告个别。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田、田山小姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.53,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你现在有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.91,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？没什么事。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.74,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那跟我来。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.04,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.42,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你抽吧田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:59.14,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,让我嚼这个就着你的烟味做最后的告别。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.81,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.36,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你真的能这么戒掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.95,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不太有信心。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你觉得我能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.91,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,别问我。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.58,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.88,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢谢你那次叫我过来。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.63,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,以后大概没机会这样聊天了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.60,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但如果在店里看到我……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.97,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,别说了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:48.77,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生我有话跟你说。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.44,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,接电话。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.99,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好、好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.32,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,喂我是佐佐木。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是的。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.70,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊体检结果？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.25,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,正打算明天去做进一步检查。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.25,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.50,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,What?。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.59,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好的我明白了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.26,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,再见。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是误诊。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:37.28,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,说我这个年龄器官非常健康。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.24,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.16,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.83,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起田山小姐对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.92,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,真是太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.29,DefaultOverlap,SASAKI,0,0,0,,让你白担心了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.00,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.17,DefaultOverlap,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真的对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.00,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.80,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不过真的太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,还能继续跟你一起抽烟呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:11.23,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对了你说有话要告诉我。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,抱歉打断了。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.94,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,现在能说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.12,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,没事。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.74,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不一定要现在。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.71,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.75,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,继续一起抽烟吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:40.34,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不过你让我这么担心可不会轻饶你。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.64,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯、嗯对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:47.01,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但我很感谢你的关心。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.31,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哼。
